data.description: This home is a must see!   Move in ready 3 bedroom, 2 bath home on .77 acre of  country living!  Hardwood floors and luxury vinyl tile.  Spacious kitchen has granite tops and a large work island. New roof, HVAC and vinyl windows.  Nice large deck on back to enjoy this fall weather!
